
            Repair - Of a broken or intermittent keyboard cable
           -----------------------------------------------------
                             on the Amiga 1200
                            -------------------
              

                              by Vaughn Tovey

                              12 January 1998


WARNING: This document is Hackware. If you do not feel confident in
opening your A1200 do not attempt this project. (see DISCLAIMER below)
          

